shared.request

Interface Request

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EventRequest, EventsRequest, FillRequest, LoadRequest, LoginRequest, PeopleRequest, PersonRequest, RegisterRequest

    public interface Request
    All objects sent from client to FMS are sent as objects implementing this interface.
    This interface simply represents the request body of an HTTP request before being converted to JSON
